#. <section class="sutta" id="an3.81"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an3.81:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 3"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 3"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an3.81:0.2"
msgid "9. Samaṇavagga"
msgstr "9. Ascetics"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an3.81:0.3"
msgid "81. Samaṇasutta"
msgstr "81. Ascetics"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi1.229"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an3.81:1.1"
msgid "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, samaṇassa samaṇiyāni samaṇakaraṇīyāni."
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are three duties of an ascetic."

msgctxt "an3.81:1.2"
msgid "Katamāni tīṇi?"
msgstr "What three?"

msgctxt "an3.81:1.3"
msgid ""
"Adhisīlasikkhāsamādānaṃ, adhicittasikkhāsamādānaṃ, adhipaññāsikkhāsamādānaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Undertaking the training in the higher ethics, the higher mind, and the "
"higher wisdom."

msgctxt "an3.81:1.4"
msgid "imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi samaṇassa samaṇiyāni samaṇakaraṇīyāni."
msgstr "These are the three duties of an ascetic."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an3.81:2.1"
msgid "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ:"
msgstr "So you should train like this:"

msgctxt "an3.81:2.2"
msgid ""
"‘tibbo no chando bhavissati adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando "
"bhavissati adhicittasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo no chando bhavissati "
"adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘We will have keen enthusiasm for undertaking the training in the higher "
"ethics, the higher mind, and the higher wisdom.’"

msgctxt "an3.81:2.3"
msgid "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti."
msgstr "That’s how you should train.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an3.81:2.4"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
